{"tid":1899787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國有參議員建議在購買醫療用品時　不能過度依賴中國","createTime":"2020-02-26T22:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T23:27:27.000Z","uid":125193,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6780c4fbb629d7e029bb0e026a494477212cef4","tid":1899787,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:11:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511097-20200227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511097-20200227.htm&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=cfe63d64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511097-20200227.htm&h=1e278b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511097-20200227.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國有參議員建議在購買醫療用品時，不能太過依賴中國。<br />\n<br />\n密蘇里州共和黨參議員霍利表示，將會提出法案，要求美國在購買醫療用品時，要尋求更多不同的來源地，不能過度依賴中國的產品。<br />\n<br />\n霍利指，新型冠狀病毒疫情提醒美國需要停止依賴中國供應醫療用品。他指，中國的疫情可能會影響美國多達150種藥物的供應，包括抗生素、原厰藥及仿製藥等，部分藥物在市場上未有替代品。霍利擔心，中國的疫情可能會造成醫療用品短缺。<br />\n<br />\n霍利星期一已經去信聯邦食品及藥物管理局主管表達關注，要求對方解釋會有何應變措施。"},{"pid":"41584ddd7f4d4d162e9a3f9a0e535396134c22ff","tid":1899787,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69224b27c9aa3b31a71182d0a65d766962f1dd56","tid":1899787,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T23:06:19.000Z","msg":"Hawley<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji